    <x-feature>
        <x-slot name="title">Residential Conveyancing</x-slot>
        <x-slot name="body">
            <x-p>Navigating the complexities of residential property
                transactions can be challenging. Our experienced residential conveyancers ensure all aspects
                of your property transaction are handled with precision and care.
            </x-p>
            <h3 class="text-gray-900 font-medium">What is Residential Conveyancing?</h3>
            <x-p>
                Residential conveyancing involves the legal process of transferring ownership of residential
                property from one person to another. This includes houses, apartments, and land designated
                for residential use.
            </x-p>
            <h3 class="text-gray-900 font-medium">Our Residential Conveyancing Services</h3>
            <x-ol>
                <li><h4 class="font-medium">Contract Preparation and Review</h4>
                    We prepare and
                    review contracts for the sale and
                    purchase of residential properties, ensuring all terms are clear and fair to protect
                    your interests.
                </li>
                <li><h4 class="font-medium">Property Searches</h4>We conduct comprehensive
                    property searches to uncover any
                    potential
                    issues that could affect your purchase, such as zoning restrictions, easements, and
                    outstanding debts.
                </li>
                <li><h4 class="font-medium">Negotiation and Advice</h4>Our team provides
                    expert advice and negotiates on your
                    behalf
                    to ensure the best possible terms for your transaction.
                </li>
                <li><h4 class="font-medium">Settlement Coordination</h4>We manage the entire
                    settlement process, ensuring all
                    conditions are met and the transfer of ownership is smooth and timely.
                </li>
            </x-ol>
        </x-slot>
