            <x-p>Our expert strata conveyancers ensure all aspects of your strata
                property transaction are handled with precision and care.
            </x-p>
            <h3 class="text-gray-900 font-medium">What is Strata Conveyancing?</h3>
            <x-p>Strata conveyancing involves the transfer of ownership for properties
                that are part of a larger complex with shared areas and facilities, governed by a body
                corporate.
            </x-p>
            <h3 class="text-gray-900 font-medium">Our Strata Conveyancing Services</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc   ml-6 space-y-4">
                <li>
                    <h4 class="text-gray-900 font-medium">Reviewing Strata Reports</h4>We provide detailed
                    reviews of strata reports, highlighting financial history, future expenditure, and the
                    current financial position of the strata corporation.
                </li>
                <li><h4 class="text-gray-900 font-medium">By-Laws and Regulations</h4>We ensure you are
                    aware of all by-laws, potential changes, and regulations affecting your strata property.
                </li>
                <li><h4 class="text-gray-900 font-medium">Financial Health Checks</h4>Our team conducts
                    thorough checks on the financial health of the strata scheme to ensure there are no
                    hidden liabilities.
                </li>
            </ul>
