        <x-slot name="title">
            Off The Plan Conveyancing
        </x-slot>
        <x-slot name="body">
            <x-p class="">Buying off the plan properties requires careful consideration and
                expertise. Our team specializes in off the plan conveyancing, ensuring you are protected
                from the moment you sign the contract to the final handover.
            </x-p>
            <h3 class="text-gray-900 font-medium">What is Off The Plan Conveyancing?</h3>
            <x-p class="">Off the plan conveyancing involves purchasing a property that is yet to
                be constructed. It requires careful contract reviews and ongoing management until the
                property is completed and ready for settlement.
            </x-p>
            <h3 class="text-gray-900 font-medium">Our Off The Plan Conveyancing Services</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc   ml-6 space-y-4">
                <li>
                    <h4 class="text-gray-900 font-medium">Contract Review</h4>We meticulously review
                    off-the-plan contracts to ensure all terms are clear and fair, protecting your interests
                    from unforeseen issues.
                </li>
                <li><h4 class="text-gray-900 font-medium">Progress Inspections</h4>We coordinate regular
                    inspections throughout the construction phase to ensure the property meets contractual
                    standards.
                </li>
                <li><h4 class="text-gray-900 font-medium">Settlement Coordination</h4>Our team manages the
                    final settlement process, ensuring all conditions are met and the property is delivered
                    as promised.
                </li>
            </ul>
        </x-slot>
